299
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:50,470
Why?

300
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:55,100
Sister...

301
00:20:58,230 --> 00:21:01,980
How could there be such a heartless elder?

302
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:06,890
