303
00:21:09,330 --> 00:21:10,850
Qin Tian!

304
00:21:10,850 --> 00:21:14,120
Why are you only telling me about my sister now?

305
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:16,520
I think your sister...

306
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:19,820
