308
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:31,150
Hello, Sile?

309
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:32,350
Where are you?

310
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:36,080
Send me your location, I'll come pick you up. All right?

311
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:43,840
